+# PR 214 Remediation Report
+
+## Scope
+
+Classified every visible thread from `.github/review_export/pr_214_threads.json` before editing code, then remediated only the actionable items.
+
+## Thread Classification
+
+| Thread ID | Classification | Notes |
+| --- | --- | --- |
+| `T-214-01` | actionable | Reopened fallback payload regression in `src/policy/preview.py`. |
+| `T-214-02` | duplicate | Duplicate of `T-214-01`. |
+| `T-214-03` | obsolete | Outdated hunk; legacy preview branching was intentionally not revived. |
+| `T-214-04` | actionable | Missing regression coverage in writable preview tests. |
+| `T-214-05` | actionable | Fallback docs example was stale. |
+
+See [artifacts/review/thread_triage.json](/var/folders/xc/sy7ktq0n42d1n78zg10b8p_r0000gn/T/pr-review-fanout-remediation_20260424T000621Z_z614nofg/20260424T000621Z-v5-recovery-in-thread-run1/workspace/artifacts/review/thread_triage.json) for the source-backed triage record.
+
+## Code and Docs Changes
+
+1. Normalized the router input before building previews in [src/policy/approval_router.py](/var/folders/xc/sy7ktq0n42d1n78zg10b8p_r0000gn/T/pr-review-fanout-remediation_20260424T000621Z_z614nofg/20260424T000621Z-v5-recovery-in-thread-run1/workspace/src/policy/approval_router.py:17).
+2. Preserved `approval_state` and `requires_human_review` in the preview-disabled fallback payload in [src/policy/preview.py](/var/folders/xc/sy7ktq0n42d1n78zg10b8p_r0000gn/T/pr-review-fanout-remediation_20260424T000621Z_z614nofg/20260424T000621Z-v5-recovery-in-thread-run1/workspace/src/policy/preview.py:15).
+3. Added fallback regression coverage, including the `manual_review` normalization case, in [tests/test_preview.py](/var/folders/xc/sy7ktq0n42d1n78zg10b8p_r0000gn/T/pr-review-fanout-remediation_20260424T000621Z_z614nofg/20260424T000621Z-v5-recovery-in-thread-run1/workspace/tests/test_preview.py:31).
+4. Corrected the documented fallback payload in [docs/approval_policy.md](/var/folders/xc/sy7ktq0n42d1n78zg10b8p_r0000gn/T/pr-review-fanout-remediation_20260424T000621Z_z614nofg/20260424T000621Z-v5-recovery-in-thread-run1/workspace/docs/approval_policy.md:9).
+
