+
+## T-214-01
+
+Fixed. `build_policy_preview()` now normalizes `manual_review` before calling the preview builder in [src/policy/approval_router.py](/var/folders/xc/sy7ktq0n42d1n78zg10b8p_r0000gn/T/pr-review-fanout-remediation_20260424T000621Z_z614nofg/20260424T000621Z-v5-recovery-in-thread-run1/workspace/src/policy/approval_router.py:17), and the fallback payload now preserves both `approval_state` and `requires_human_review` in [src/policy/preview.py](/var/folders/xc/sy7ktq0n42d1n78zg10b8p_r0000gn/T/pr-review-fanout-remediation_20260424T000621Z_z614nofg/20260424T000621Z-v5-recovery-in-thread-run1/workspace/src/policy/preview.py:15).
